{"tid":2052054,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻廢老貪平轉左中国聯通","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T10:19:39.000Z","uid":57308,"like":197,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2d15718879e40eaa566e98ace8324566c41046","tid":2052054,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先打返嚟搵我救命<br />\n話以前用smt 打出打入都係即收到咁滯<br />\n而家中聯通要等十幾秒，試過幾次對面以為打唔通收線算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出入lift 又要等好耐先有返訊號<br />\n平時搭黨鐵又收得差<br />\n問我有冇得cut 咗佢轉第二間<br />\n我扮嘢問佢份合約擺邊我攞嚟睇睇，隔咗陣專登嚇佢，冇架啦cut 要罰好多錢，遲啲可能仲會上嗰個咩大灣區信用名單要扣分<br />\n佢忍唔住開始鬧呢間乜撚嘢垃圾公司嚟<br />\n我即刻喝住佢，話呢間国企嚟，同政府部門差唔多，立咗国安法你仲敢鬧，想坐監？<br />\n佢問我點算<br />\n我：咪忍兩年囉，你記得鬧都好返嚟鬧，唔好喺出面鬧，俾人聽到要拉<br />\n佢死死氣咁收左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0aef408db971de673b2781accb9ae500da50162","tid":2052054,"uid":275447,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"聯通都用，仲衰過支那移動"},{"pid":"a4362862e5b8483e0310d47d9e261b53462d25f8","tid":2052054,"uid":1095,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"應該有合約冷靜期？"},{"pid":"e8615aafdb4817f429a6e0ca5716a56621a4af58","tid":2052054,"uid":57308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4362862e5b8483e0310d47d9e261b53462d25f8","tid":2052054,"uid":1095,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"應該有合約冷靜期？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"開始用緊都有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d954a8b1c1da504e89b3ab61dd54eeda7e6211","tid":2052054,"uid":57308,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"a4362862e5b8483e0310d47d9e261b53462d25f8","tid